export const categories = {
    ERROR: "error",
    API_ERROR: "api-error",
    WINNER: "rtc winner",
    NON_RTC: "non-rtc winner",
    NON_WINNER: "non-winner",
    REJECTED: "rejected",
    ENVIRONMENT: "environment",
    KYC_ACCEPTED: "kyc-accepted",
    KYC_REJECTED: "kyc-rejected",
    TICKET_SCAN_VELOCITY: "ticket-scan-threshold"
}
